item.title: Sennheiser PC 3 Chat Stereo 2 x 3.5 mm Headset
item.dc:creator: admin
item.description:
• Compatibility: PC / Soft phone
  • Lightweight stereo headset
  • Unidirectional microphone
  • Plug-and-play simplicity
item.content:encoded:
Easy-to-use, lightweight, and affordable, the PC 3 CHAT on-ear stereo headset is built for e-learning and staying in touch. Stereo construction keeps you focused on the task at hand, while a noise-canceling microphone ensures that every word you say is communicated clearly.

Stereo ear-pieces keep you focused, while a low weight ensures comfort

Engineered to last and withstand the rigors of frequent use

A passive noise-canceling microphone prioritizes clear communication Plug in the PC 3 CHAT via two 3.5 mm jacks, and you are ready to go

Lightweight USB stereo headset

Stereo ear-pieces keep you focused, while a low weight ensures comfort
